import React from 'react';
import {
    DataProviderContext,
    TestContext,
    TranslationProvider,
} from 'react-admin';

import { i18nProvider } from '../i18n';
import { ApiList } from './ApiList';

export default {
    title: 'Apis/ApiList',
    component: ApiList,
};

export const Default = () => (
    <TestContext initialState={initialState}>
        <DataProviderContext.Provider value={dataProvider}>
            <TranslationProvider i18nProvider={i18nProvider('en')}>
                <ApiList
                    basePath="/apis"
                    resource="apis"
                    hasCreate={false}
                    hasShow={false}
                    hasEdit={false}
                    hasList
                />
            </TranslationProvider>
        </DataProviderContext.Provider>
    </TestContext>
);

const ids = [
    '1e2bbc39-d1e3-4323-a252-8d5345cbdfbf',

const dataProvider = {
    getList: () =>
        Promise.resolve({
            data: Object.values(data),
            total: 6,

const initialState = {
    admin: {
        resources: {
            apis: {
                data,
                list: {
                    ids,
